WEBVTT

00:00:27.636 --> 00:00:30.847
JULY THIRTY ONE, NINETEEN NINETY SIX.

00:00:30.847 --> 00:00:34.847
SURVIVOR: ISRAEL FINGUR. INTERVIEWER: PHYLLIS DREAZEN.

00:00:34.847 --> 00:00:37.451
CHICAGO, ILLINOIS, U.S.A.

00:00:37.710 --> 00:00:40.117
 THE LANGUAGE OF THE INTERVIEW IS YIDDISH.

00:00:41.862 --> 00:00:48.018
JULY THIRTY ONE, NINETEEN NINETY SIX. I'M PHYLLIS DREAZEN. I'LL BE SPEAKING WITH ISRAEL FINGURT.

00:00:48.139 --> 00:00:51.255
WE'RE IN CHICAGO. WE'LL BE SPEAKING IN YIDDISH.

00:00:53.404 --> 00:00:54.714
vi heystu?

00:00:55.345 --> 00:00:57.115
ISRAEL Fingurt.

00:00:57.420 --> 00:00:59.540
un vi hostu geheysn in der heym?

00:00:59.910 --> 00:01:02.723
oykh ISRAEL. oykh Fingurt.

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:04.012
andere nemen?

00:01:04.221 --> 00:01:05.075
NO.

00:01:05.247 --> 00:01:07.326
kh'hob nisht gehat keyn ander nomen.

00:01:07.562 --> 00:01:10.529
kurts-nemen? neyn?

00:01:08.647 --> 00:01:11.049
n- neyn. neyn.

00:01:11.807 --> 00:01:16.347
me fleg zogn ⟨Yis- Srol⟩, Yisroel, nor oykhet ISRAEL.

00:01:15.658 --> 00:01:16.819
Srolik?

00:01:16.347 --> 00:01:17.844
Srolik, Srol.

00:01:17.229 --> 00:01:18.533
yo.

00:01:20.366 --> 00:01:22.524
 ven bistu geborn gevorn?

00:01:22.430 --> 00:01:27.200
kh'bin geboyrn gevorn in toyznt nayn hundert tsvey un tsvontsik.

00:01:27.007 --> 00:01:28.856
vi alt bistu haynt?

00:01:28.623 --> 00:01:31.147
haynt bin ikh fir un zibetsik yor.

00:01:32.385 --> 00:01:34.404
un vu bistu geborn gevorn?

00:01:34.275 --> 00:01:36.423
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn in a dorf

00:01:36.423 --> 00:01:38.032
fun mitl Besarabye,

00:01:38.190 --> 00:01:39.661
⟨Skortsen⟩,

00:01:40.435 --> 00:01:43.038
Orkheyer gegnt.

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:47.684
dos iz geven a, a dorf

00:01:47.708 --> 00:01:49.018
vu es hobn gevoynt,

00:01:50.408 --> 00:01:51.795
kimat

00:01:51.795 --> 00:01:53.054
a fuftsik

00:01:53.054 --> 00:01:54.587
mishpokhes fun yidn.

00:01:55.065 --> 00:01:56.696
geven a shil.

00:01:56.196 --> 00:01:58.238
un fun goyim, vifl?

00:01:57.947 --> 00:01:59.990
goyim iz geven ariber finef hundert.

00:02:00.212 --> 00:02:00.915
yo.

00:02:01.562 --> 00:02:04.087
geven a shil in dorf. s'iz geven a kheyder.

00:02:04.768 --> 00:02:06.209
geven a shoykhet.

00:02:07.030 --> 00:02:08.071
a mikve?

00:02:07.782 --> 00:02:10.190
 neyn. neyn.

00:02:11.097 --> 00:02:12.442
..

00:02:12.442 --> 00:02:13.913
vos nokh?

00:02:13.813 --> 00:02:15.140
talmud-toyre?

00:02:13.913 --> 00:02:15.074
di yidn...

00:02:15.940 --> 00:02:17.428
a talmud-toyre?

00:02:17.366 --> 00:02:19.466
a talmud-toyre? der kheyder, kheyder.

00:02:17.876 --> 00:02:18.666
a yeshive?

00:02:18.727 --> 00:02:19.770
⟨oh, kh-⟩ kheyder?

00:02:19.568 --> 00:02:20.962
kheyder iz geven.

00:02:20.125 --> 00:02:21.654
un oykh yeshive?

00:02:21.475 --> 00:02:22.177
NO.

00:02:22.117 --> 00:02:22.595
NO.

00:02:22.456 --> 00:02:25.325
⟨NO⟩, keyn yeshive iz nisht geven in dorf.

00:02:27.685 --> 00:02:28.708
..

00:02:29.625 --> 00:02:30.851
un vos nokh?

00:02:31.093 --> 00:02:33.044
 di yidn,

00:02:34.198 --> 00:02:36.284
 zenen geven shomre-shabes,

00:02:37.135 --> 00:02:38.715
flegn geyn in shil arayn.

00:02:39.362 --> 00:02:42.697
⟨un⟩ tomer iz eyn yid nisht gekumen in shil shabes,

00:02:42.805 --> 00:02:45.265
fleg ⟨men dem⟩ tsveytn tog geyn fregn,

00:02:45.265 --> 00:02:48.215
"Yankl, Berl, far vos bistu nisht gekumen in shil arayn?"

00:02:49.504 --> 00:02:54.150
azoy, s'iz geven a, ⟨nu, k-⟩, a koshere, kehile.

00:02:54.150 --> 00:03:00.783
s'iz nisht geven keyn yidn apikorsim, zoln nisht, ophitn keyn toyre, zoln nisht ophitn keyn shabes,

00:03:00.783 --> 00:03:03.724
tsi me zol nisht esn kosher. s'iz nisht geven azoyne yidn.

00:03:03.865 --> 00:03:08.097
un di yidn, hobn zikh opgegebn, s'iz geven shnayders,

00:03:08.097 --> 00:03:09.498
shusters,

00:03:09.498 --> 00:03:12.841
 stolyers, vos zey hobn gemakht,

00:03:13.062 --> 00:03:14.710
 benk,

00:03:14.918 --> 00:03:16.667
tishn, fentster,

00:03:16.690 --> 00:03:21.071
 s'iz geven, zey hobn gehandlt,

00:03:21.263 --> 00:03:24.142
gekoyft tvue bay di kristn,

00:03:24.165 --> 00:03:27.655
floymen, epl, barn,

00:03:27.655 --> 00:03:28.732
nis.

00:03:28.873 --> 00:03:33.116
 geven, zey hobn gehat kleytn,

00:03:33.379 --> 00:03:34.725
kleyne kleytlekh,

00:03:34.725 --> 00:03:37.866
n⟨or,⟩ dos ⟨iz oykh⟩ geven dos yidish...

00:03:38.931 --> 00:03:40.716
un vi azoy iz geven

00:03:40.716 --> 00:03:42.334
bay dir in hoyz?

00:03:42.508 --> 00:03:44.766
a hoyz? an APARTMENT?

00:03:42.584 --> 00:03:51.344
bay mir, ⟨m- mir in⟩ hoyz, dos iz geven, undzer mishpokhe, mir hobn, mayn tate hot zikh opgegebn mit erd-arbet.

00:03:51.486 --> 00:03:53.285
mir hobn gevaksn tabak,

00:03:54.186 --> 00:03:59.696
un dos iz geven a arbet vos me heybt on fun friling un me endikt, ⟨⟩, shpet vinter.

00:03:59.696 --> 00:04:02.393
a gants yor iz men farnemen in der zakh.

00:04:02.393 --> 00:04:04.558
nor a sh- di shtub iz geven a koshere,

00:04:04.699 --> 00:04:07.438
mayn tate,

00:04:07.438 --> 00:04:10.258
bay tog un oyf der nakht hot er tomed gedavnt.

00:04:10.453 --> 00:04:15.425
nor az di, ikh, mayn muter iz geshtorbn,

00:04:15.482 --> 00:04:18.294
 ven ikh bin geven fun fir mit a halbn yor,

00:04:18.874 --> 00:04:22.209
un dernokh dem hot mayn tate khasene gehat far a ander froy,

00:04:22.553 --> 00:04:24.707
oykhet fun, fun dem dorf,

00:04:24.707 --> 00:04:26.898
un zi hot undz shoyn ⟨oy-⟩ oyfgetsoygn.

00:04:26.518 --> 00:04:28.292
un zi iz geven a gute?

00:04:28.135 --> 00:04:30.337
geven a gute ma- a gute froy.

00:04:30.337 --> 00:04:32.483
mir flegn zi afile rufn "mame."

00:04:32.863 --> 00:04:35.089
ikh bin geven mit mayn, mayn eltern bruder.

00:04:36.475 --> 00:04:39.979
un fun finef yor hob ikh ongehoybn shoyn geyn lernen in kheyder.

00:04:40.322 --> 00:04:43.707
far vos fun finef? vayl mayn, elterer bruder iz gegangen.

00:04:43.707 --> 00:04:46.808
abi ikh zol... vos zhe, ikh'l blaybn aleyn in der heym? gey ikh oykh⟨et⟩.

00:04:46.836 --> 00:04:49.865
un azoy bin ikh geblibn in kheyder fun finef yor,

00:04:50.498 --> 00:04:51.752
un kh'hob gelernt...

00:04:51.494 --> 00:04:53.680
vi azoy hobn zey ale geheysn?

00:04:53.839 --> 00:04:54.592
ver?

00:04:54.902 --> 00:04:57.022
mayn tate hot geheysn Shloyme,

00:04:57.771 --> 00:04:59.773
di mame hot geheysn Leye,

00:04:59.813 --> 00:05:01.849
un mayn bruder iz Yeshue.

00:05:02.968 --> 00:05:04.075
..

00:05:03.171 --> 00:05:05.202
vifl brider hostu gehat?

00:05:05.112 --> 00:05:09.561
eyn, eyn bruder, Yeshue, iz geven mayn eygener bruder,

00:05:09.567 --> 00:05:12.463
un kh'hob a bruder in ISRAEL, Shmuel.

00:05:12.553 --> 00:05:14.994
yener iz fun der tsveyter muter.

00:05:21.075 --> 00:05:27.701
ikh hob gelernt, in kheyder hob ikh gelernt yidish, ivrit hobn mir oykh gelernt, biz fertsn yor.

00:05:28.602 --> 00:05:34.325
un, paralel mit dem bin ikh gegangen in der federal shul,

00:05:34.325 --> 00:05:37.078
oyf, rumenish. hob ikh gelernt rumenish oykh.

00:05:37.512 --> 00:05:41.708
azoy arum az, keyn tsayt iz nisht geven oyf,

00:05:42.608 --> 00:05:43.732
oyf tsu,

00:05:44.127 --> 00:05:45.656
tsu rashn.

00:05:46.192 --> 00:05:48.091
ober tsu shpiln?

00:05:47.853 --> 00:05:49.217
shpiln, a bisele.

00:05:49.375 --> 00:05:50.898
nisht keyn sakh.

00:05:52.176 --> 00:05:53.570
vifl shtunde

00:05:54.117 --> 00:05:57.638
yedn tog hostu gelernt in di tsvey shuln?

00:05:56.112 --> 00:06:03.631
nu, mir hobn gelernt, mir hobn gelernt, in der rumenisher shkole hobn mir gelernt, fir, fir shtundes,

00:06:03.631 --> 00:06:08.623
un in der yidisher oykhet fir-finef shtundes in, in y- in, in tog.

00:06:08.680 --> 00:06:13.853
un akhuts dem fleg men darfn aheymkumen, oyf der nakht un makhn di,

00:06:13.853 --> 00:06:20.561
di, ⟨⟩, lektsyes oyf morgn, vegn, i vegn dem kheyder, i vegn der, rumenisher shkole.

00:06:21.201 --> 00:06:24.671
un di shuln zaynen geven nont tsu dayn hoyz?

00:06:25.234 --> 00:06:25.988
neyn,

00:06:25.988 --> 00:06:29.426
nisht azoy nont, nor s'iz nisht geven vayt. vegn kinder heyst nisht vayt.

00:06:29.426 --> 00:06:31.404
mir zenen ⟨zikh⟩ geven yunge kinder.

00:06:34.228 --> 00:06:40.398
azoy arum az, ikh hob teykef gevaksn mit dray, mit dray leshoynes.

00:06:42.632 --> 00:06:45.039
nu, dos iz di, dos dorf.

00:06:45.501 --> 00:06:47.179
fun fertsn yor....

00:06:45.518 --> 00:06:47.927
dertsey- dertseyl undz

00:06:47.927 --> 00:06:50.354
epes vegn shabes un yontev.

00:06:50.648 --> 00:06:52.786
vi azoy hot men gemakht?

00:06:51.981 --> 00:06:56.548
nu, shabes hot men gevust az fraytik-tsu-nakht darf men geyn in shil arayn,

00:06:56.925 --> 00:06:59.450
shabes in der fri darf men geyn in shil arayn.

00:06:59.878 --> 00:07:04.782
nokh, nokhn, ⟨nu⟩, nokhn, nokh der shil

00:07:05.346 --> 00:07:06.825
hot men opgeesn,

00:07:07.050 --> 00:07:12.123
un m'iz gegangen, a bisele tsu di kroyvim, tsu di bakente, tsu...

00:07:12.123 --> 00:07:14.224
un mir kinder zenen gegangen zikh shpiln.

00:07:14.172 --> 00:07:15.921
vos hostu gegesn

00:07:16.433 --> 00:07:17.629
shabes?

00:07:16.467 --> 00:07:21.439
? shabes? shabes iz tomed geven a hun a gekoylete baym shoykhet

00:07:21.698 --> 00:07:23.801
un a tsimes

00:07:24.010 --> 00:07:28.065
un a, a rosele,

00:07:28.065 --> 00:07:30.838
a tsholnt. dos alding iz geven shabes.

00:07:32.143 --> 00:07:34.258
⟨un⟩ kikhelekh ⟨tsur tey⟩.

00:07:35.890 --> 00:07:38.347
froyen zaynen gegangen in shul?

00:07:39.180 --> 00:07:44.213
 fri,... ⟨⟩ nayn a zeyger hot men ongehoybn,...

00:07:41.965 --> 00:07:44.389
NO, froy, di froyen.

00:07:48.529 --> 00:07:49.569
meydlekh?

00:07:49.913 --> 00:07:51.022
ah!

00:07:51.022 --> 00:07:56.348
 di, neyn. di meydlekh zenen nisht gegangen, di vayber zenen oykh nisht gegangen in shil arayn shabes.

00:07:56.348 --> 00:08:01.696
gegangen nor di, di mener mit di kinder, di, di yinglekh zenen gegangen shabes.

00:08:01.696 --> 00:08:07.541
un mir, mir hobn, fun finef yor, fun fir mit a halbn yor hob ikh ongehoybn zogn kadesh,

00:08:08.610 --> 00:08:14.133
vayl mayn mame iz geshtorbn ⟨ve- ⟩, ven ikh bin geven fir mit a halbn yor, un teykef hobn mir ongehoybn zogn kadesh.

00:08:14.133 --> 00:08:16.446
hot undz undzer zeyde oysgelernt kadesh,

00:08:16.446 --> 00:08:19.674
un mir beyde flegn shteyn un zogn kadesh.

00:08:18.752 --> 00:08:19.657
uhuh.

00:08:22.279 --> 00:08:23.415
yontev...

00:08:23.415 --> 00:08:27.517
ale yontoyvim zenen geven bay di yidn,

00:08:27.517 --> 00:08:32.168
freylekhe yontoyvim. s'iz geven UNK ale yontoyvim azoy vi, azoy vi s'geher tsu zayn.

00:08:32.168 --> 00:08:33.528
 di,

00:08:34.157 --> 00:08:38.611
 di shil iz, hot gearbet, s'iz gekumen rosheshone,

00:08:38.611 --> 00:08:40.914
yom-kiper, sukes,

00:08:40.914 --> 00:08:44.255
iz, yeder tog geven di shil ofn

00:08:44.255 --> 00:08:53.377
un me fleg kumen davenen, s'iz geven, UNK tomer, a shteyger, sukes, ⟨iz⟩ hot men gekoyft an, esreg mit a lulev,

00:08:53.377 --> 00:08:57.036
un yeder tog ⟨zenen⟩ gekumen un m'hot gebentsht esreg mit lulev.

00:08:57.210 --> 00:08:58.945
hot gehat a, a suke

00:08:57.345 --> 00:08:58.314
..

00:08:58.945 --> 00:09:00.242
bay dir in...?

00:08:59.337 --> 00:09:01.879
a suke. a suke iz geven in shil.

00:09:01.952 --> 00:09:07.589
mir hobn nisht gehat undzer eygene shtub. mir hobn gehat a, a, mir hobn gedungen a shtub,

00:09:07.589 --> 00:09:10.054
hobn mir nisht gekent makhn keyn suke.

00:09:10.221 --> 00:09:14.581
nor ⟨es iz⟩ geven, bay a sakh yidn iz geven sukes in der heym oykhet, yo.

00:09:16.310 --> 00:09:18.961
un di andere yontoyvim oykhet, di,

00:09:18.829 --> 00:09:20.155
peysekh?

00:09:18.961 --> 00:09:20.186
,

00:09:20.186 --> 00:09:23.961
peysekh, peysekh iz, geven nor der kosherer peysekh.

00:09:23.961 --> 00:09:28.991
bay undz iz nisht geven keyn matses. m'hot nisht gebakn in, in dorf keyn matses. fleg men brengen di matses

00:09:28.991 --> 00:09:34.500
fun a ander shtot, tsi fun ⟨Orkhey⟩, tsi fun ⟨Kapresht⟩ fleg men brengen matses.

00:09:34.500 --> 00:09:36.168
un,

00:09:36.343 --> 00:09:40.643
 un, praven dem seyder vi s'geher tsu zayn

00:09:40.643 --> 00:09:42.652
mit, mit ale...

00:09:41.288 --> 00:09:42.750
groysn seyder?

00:09:42.652 --> 00:09:48.698
ha? a seyder, di, yeder mishpokhe hot gehat zayn seyder, ⟨zenen mir azoy,⟩ m'hot zikh nit tsu- yo, m'hot zikh nit tsunoyfgenemen ⟨keyn sakh⟩.

00:09:45.523 --> 00:09:46.756
far zikh?

00:09:46.756 --> 00:09:47.896
yo.

00:09:48.698 --> 00:09:52.335
bay undz fleg⟨n⟩, fleg, az der, mayn, tate,

00:09:52.375 --> 00:09:58.244
, az mayn zeyde iz geshtorbn, flegn shoyn tsun undzer seyder kumen di bobe

00:09:58.244 --> 00:10:02.066
mit, der, un ir tokhter,

00:10:02.066 --> 00:10:08.597
heyst mayn, mayn foter's, shvester mit di kinder flegn oykh kumen tsun undz in seyder arayn.

00:10:08.597 --> 00:10:12.408
nu, fregn di kashes mit ale, mit a- mit ale...

00:10:11.968 --> 00:10:13.590
AFIKOMEN?

00:10:12.408 --> 00:10:15.943
mit afikoymen, un darf men UNK farganvenen,

00:10:14.804 --> 00:10:15.911
handlen?

00:10:15.943 --> 00:10:20.651
darf men ⟨im⟩ ganvenen dem afikoymen un, der tate vil nisht, az me zol im tsuganvenen.

00:10:20.674 --> 00:10:22.773
nu, s'iz geven, s'iz geven freylekh.

00:10:23.593 --> 00:10:27.622
un, ale teg peysekh hot ⟨men⟩ opgehit peysekh.

00:10:27.998 --> 00:10:29.747
 m'hot,

00:10:29.989 --> 00:10:32.937
gemakht malayklekh fun kartoflyes.

00:10:32.937 --> 00:10:38.093
m'hot, matse, ⟨, mit, ⟩, fun matse-mel kezlekh gemakht,...

00:10:36.895 --> 00:10:38.832
uhuh. gebrokht?

00:10:38.093 --> 00:10:40.040
gemakht, yo. ales.

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:39.910
yo.

00:10:40.603 --> 00:10:42.669
dos iz geven der peysekh.

00:10:43.253 --> 00:10:45.259
nu, shvues...

00:10:43.999 --> 00:10:45.397
simkhes-... yo?

00:10:45.259 --> 00:10:47.158
shvues, azoy vi shvues,

00:10:47.158 --> 00:10:54.047
⟨iz⟩, mit grins opge- oysge-, -sheynt der, di shtub mit,

00:10:54.174 --> 00:10:55.864
,

00:10:56.043 --> 00:10:59.244
mit, grins oyf der erd, mit,

00:10:59.244 --> 00:11:03.749
 oyf, oyf di vent, UNK ⟨iz⟩ grins oykhet.

00:11:03.992 --> 00:11:08.863
blintses? vos hostu gegesn? blintses? ⟨⟩

00:11:04.380 --> 00:11:06.376
nu, un oykhet geyn in shil arayn....

00:11:07.924 --> 00:11:13.571
 nu, pey-, shvues hot men gedarft milkhike, milkhike maykholim esn:

00:11:13.712 --> 00:11:14.955
kreplekh,

00:11:15.282 --> 00:11:20.254
 beygelekh fun, mit rayz, beygelekh fun, kez.

00:11:20.783 --> 00:11:22.025
dos iz geven.

00:11:22.048 --> 00:11:27.339
mir hobn gehat, in der heym hobn mir gehat tsign. iz milkh⟨ik⟩ iz geven bay undz tomed in shtub,

00:11:27.339 --> 00:11:30.752
kosher milkhiks, iz fleg men makhn aldings vos m'hot gedarft.

00:11:31.971 --> 00:11:34.192
 simkhes-toyre.

00:11:34.192 --> 00:11:38.698
nu, simkhes-toyre der, vegn di kinder iz geven gor a groyser yontev.

00:11:38.755 --> 00:11:41.300
ale flegn zikh ontun sheyn

00:11:41.300 --> 00:11:44.000
un nemen, iz geven, ⟨me fleg⟩ brengen,

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:46.559
 fonen, fondlekh, degls,

00:11:46.559 --> 00:11:49.880
un oyf di fondlekh shteln an epele a royts,

00:11:49.880 --> 00:11:53.642
un oyfn epele a, a likhtl,

00:11:53.642 --> 00:11:58.899
un geyn mit hakofes, mit a, mit ale, mit ale mentshn fun velkhe zenen gegangen di hakofes,

00:11:58.899 --> 00:12:02.443
iz hobn di kinder oykh gedarft nokhgeyn mit di, mit di, mit di li⟨f⟩tn, mit di

00:12:02.443 --> 00:12:04.618
