00:23:10.102 --> 00:23:13.385
flegn zey kumen, betn a shtikele, a bisele tutin oyf tsu reykhern.

00:23:13.385 --> 00:23:15.351
epes in a tog iz geven aza geshikhte:

00:23:15.351 --> 00:23:17.390
geven a miting in dorf,

00:23:17.464 --> 00:23:24.731
un, di kristn hobn zikh tsunoyfgenemen oyf dem miting. s'hot, geredt der, onfirer, der ⟨POPOI⟩ hot, geredt,

00:23:24.805 --> 00:23:27.870
 fun zayn PARTII, fun zayn partey,

00:23:27.977 --> 00:23:37.556
un, nokh dem, nokhn miting kumt eyner tsum papn, tatn un zogt, "gib mir a bisele, tabak oyf tsu reykhern."

00:23:37.680 --> 00:23:42.680
zogt er, "bist nor vos geven oyfn miting! host geshrign, ⟨host⟩ geshrign, "JOS JIDANII!""

00:23:42.680 --> 00:23:49.706
heyst, aroptsunemen di yidn, zol men fartraybn fun dane⟨n⟩. "un itster bist gekumen tsu mir nokh, nokh tabak?"

00:23:49.712 --> 00:23:51.257
zogt er,

00:23:51.257 --> 00:23:56.253
", dos vos dortn iz geven der miting, iz dos geven ⟨az-⟩ m'hot ⟨e⟩s azoy gedarft,

00:23:56.253 --> 00:24:03.551
nor mir lebn zikh do. m- mir lebn zikh mit aykh. vos ⟨zhe iz do-⟩..? nu, s'kert zikh nit on. do, ikh darf hobn erd bay im. ikh darf nit hobn zayn,

00:24:03.551 --> 00:24:05.590
zayn partey. ikh darf hobn zayn erd."

00:24:12.915 --> 00:24:14.982
a gutn lebn,?

00:24:14.947 --> 00:24:16.526
a gut lebn?

00:24:16.527 --> 00:24:20.508
nisht azoy gut geven. s'iz geven, etlekhe yidn iz geven gvirim,

00:24:21.049 --> 00:24:25.194
⟨vos⟩ zey hobn, ⟨hobn⟩ gehat a sakh, gute kleytn mit,

00:24:25.386 --> 00:24:28.186
tvues mit, erd, mit aldings,

00:24:28.186 --> 00:24:33.513
nor di, di iberike mentshn hobn zikh azoy durkhge- durkhgevorfn durkh, durkhn lebn.

00:24:33.513 --> 00:24:36.785
nisht, iz geven eyner, a,

00:24:36.785 --> 00:24:40.224
 ⟨Yirmie Gori⟩, hot er gehat a,

00:24:41.333 --> 00:24:44.342
a masleboyke flegn ⟨m⟩ir zogn, oyf tsu makhn,

00:24:44.342 --> 00:24:46.592
oyf tsu makhn,

00:24:47.121 --> 00:24:48.127
OIL,

00:24:48.167 --> 00:24:49.971
fun,

00:24:49.971 --> 00:24:51.457
fun royzn.

00:24:51.778 --> 00:25:02.738
nu, iz, dos iz geven de- der... nor vayter iz nisht geven azoy, di yidn, di, efsher iz geven tsen, azoy vi, azelkhe, zey hobn gelebt beser a bisl fun di andere.

00:25:02.738 --> 00:25:06.218
nor di, di yidn hobn ⟨ts-⟩ gelebt azoy mitl.

00:25:07.422 --> 00:25:09.523
un kabtsonim oykh.

00:25:09.700 --> 00:25:11.229
un dayn familye?

00:25:11.522 --> 00:25:13.349
mayn familye iz geven oykhet a mitl.

00:25:13.349 --> 00:25:17.206
⟨un⟩ az, az m'hot gut batsolt farn tutin, farn tabak,

00:25:17.206 --> 00:25:18.881
iz, geven gut.

00:25:18.881 --> 00:25:22.131
az m'hot nisht gut batsolt farn tabak, iz men geven a kabtsn.

00:25:22.170 --> 00:25:27.044
un akhuts dem, bay mayn tatn iz, hot er nokh gehat khoyves fun, ven,

00:25:27.044 --> 00:25:30.267
nu, nokh dem vos mayn, mame iz, iz geshtorbn.

00:25:30.267 --> 00:25:34.325
hot er gehat khoyves mitn, mekaber zayn, mit ⟨ot do⟩, mit ⟨de-⟩...

00:25:34.325 --> 00:25:39.488
iz hot er, fleg er yeder yor darfn opgebn di, fun di khoyves oykhet tsu bislekh.

00:25:39.488 --> 00:25:42.060
azoy arum az mir hobn gelebt azoy, nisht,

00:25:42.302 --> 00:25:45.722
nisht ⟨tsu tsu⟩, nor geshlept dos lebn.

00:25:46.656 --> 00:25:49.012
un yeshive iz geven in ⟨Skortsen⟩?

00:25:48.698 --> 00:25:49.881
neyn.

00:25:49.881 --> 00:25:51.762
yeshive iz geven in Keshenev.

00:25:51.938 --> 00:25:57.508
in fertsn y-, ven ikh bin alt gevorn fertsn yor, bin ikh gegangen in, geforn in der yeshive arayn.

00:25:57.809 --> 00:25:59.523
Keshenever yeshive...

00:25:57.962 --> 00:26:01.432
un vi vayt iz Keshenev fun ⟨Skortsen⟩?

00:25:59.952 --> 00:26:03.705
Keshenev iz a akhtsik, a akhtsik kilometer, a,

00:26:03.705 --> 00:26:05.873
a finef un fuftsik mayl

00:26:05.873 --> 00:26:08.442
fun, fun undzer dorf.

00:26:11.023 --> 00:26:14.538
ikh bin gekumen ahin tsu, in der yeshive.

00:26:15.546 --> 00:26:19.590
 dos is geven a yeshive, aza a gerimte yeshive

00:26:19.832 --> 00:26:24.756
oyf gants, dorem B- B- Besarabye. flegn kumen ⟨fun⟩, khevre

00:26:24.756 --> 00:26:28.384
fun, Yas, fun, Izmail,

00:26:28.384 --> 00:26:30.621
fun, Akerman,

00:26:30.621 --> 00:26:37.049
fun Tshernovits, fun Keshenev, fun di d- fun di shtetlekh fun, fun Besarabye flegn kumen ahin tsu

00:26:37.049 --> 00:26:37.935
lernen.

00:26:38.023 --> 00:26:39.615
es...

00:26:38.040 --> 00:26:40.278
vi hot geheysn der rosh-yeshive?

00:26:40.622 --> 00:26:47.294
⟨,⟩ bald aykh zogn. d⟨er⟩, keyn, di yeshive hot geheysn Perl-, Perlmuter's yeshive.

00:26:47.490 --> 00:26:53.542
 der rosh-ye- keyn rosh-yeshive iz nisht geven. s'iz geven a KOMITET, velkher hot ongefirt mit der yeshive,

00:26:53.599 --> 00:26:58.346
un tsi-, tsishn ale gliders fun dem komitet, s'iz geven der,

00:26:58.346 --> 00:27:03.060
 hoypt, rov fun, Besarabye, RAV HARASHI fun Besarabye,

00:27:03.066 --> 00:27:05.512
 Yehude-Leyb Tsirlson.

00:27:05.884 --> 00:27:09.306
nu, Yehude-Leyb Tsirlson oyf,

00:27:09.306 --> 00:27:13.120
fun, fun Tsirlson oyf tsu redn iz darf, iz do a sakh tsu redn,

00:27:13.120 --> 00:27:17.371
vayl s'iz geven a, a mentsh, azoy vi me zogt, i, i tsu got, i tsu layt.

00:27:17.371 --> 00:27:19.732
 ale,

00:27:20.329 --> 00:27:24.004
 poyers, ale mentshn fun di derfer, az zey hobn gedarft epes a shayle,

00:27:24.004 --> 00:27:29.902
flegn nisht geyn tsu keyn rebe, flegn nisht geyn tsu... es iz geven bay undz in di, in Besarabye iz geven rabonim oykhet.

00:27:29.902 --> 00:27:34.442
nor ⟨zey⟩ kumen tsu Tsirlson, ⟨vayl⟩ m'hot gevust, az Tsirlson vet ⟨azoy⟩ gibn an eytse,

00:27:34.442 --> 00:27:36.403
iz dos a eytse vi s'geher tsu zayn.

00:27:36.403 --> 00:27:39.075
er iz geven shtark a, a ongenemener mentsh.

00:27:40.309 --> 00:27:42.631
er hot gehat a groysn AVTORITET in,

00:27:42.756 --> 00:27:44.488
 tsishn di yidn.

00:27:44.545 --> 00:27:46.433
m'hot gegleybt in im.

00:27:46.433 --> 00:27:51.613
nu, nor er iz take geven, draysik yor iz er geven hoypt rov fun gants Besarabye.

00:27:54.855 --> 00:27:57.933
iz, iz derfar,

00:27:58.011 --> 00:28:00.452
az,

00:28:00.452 --> 00:28:05.320
az a yid hot gehat epes, tsu fregn, iz er tomed gekumen tsu Tsirlson zikh

00:28:05.320 --> 00:28:07.924
hobn a eytse mit im, makhn a,

00:28:07.924 --> 00:28:11.358
 epes a droshe UNK, aldings, vi es geher tsu zayn.

00:28:10.887 --> 00:28:13.041
vos hostu gelernt in yeshive?

00:28:13.522 --> 00:28:16.823
nu, in der yeshive hob ikh gelernt,

00:28:16.823 --> 00:28:21.697
nu, gemore hobn mir ⟨dokh⟩, hobn mir ongelernt, mishnayes, un vos...

00:28:22.029 --> 00:28:24.132
 shulkhn-orekh.

00:28:24.132 --> 00:28:25.514
un akhuts dem,

00:28:25.514 --> 00:28:32.823
dos UNK itster lernt men nisht in di yeshives... ikh veys nit vi azoy in ISRAEL, nor, do in, in Amerike,

00:28:32.823 --> 00:28:34.188
lernt men nisht keyn,

00:28:34.188 --> 00:28:39.397
, neviim rishoynim un neviim akhroynim.

00:28:39.397 --> 00:28:40.428
me lernt nisht!

00:28:40.502 --> 00:28:44.158
nor, bay undz in der yeshive hobn mir oysgelernt ale neviim,

00:28:44.299 --> 00:28:49.206
UNK onheybndik fun, fun Yeshue un endikn mit Yekheskl, mit ale,

00:28:49.206 --> 00:28:53.214
Yi- Yirmyohu un, Yeshaye, un Yekheskl, un,

00:28:53.214 --> 00:28:55.425
ale, ale neviim hobn mir gelernt.

00:28:55.425 --> 00:28:56.949
nor ikh trakht azoy:

00:28:57.259 --> 00:28:59.463
az... ot dos iz mayn meynung:

00:28:59.503 --> 00:29:01.778
az oyf tsu lernen di neviim,

00:29:01.778 --> 00:29:04.239
darf men kenen gut ivrit,

00:29:03.790 --> 00:29:04.577
yo.

00:29:04.768 --> 00:29:11.086
un, do viln zey nisht azoy zikh ayn⟨t⟩- in, aynzinken in, in de- in dem ivrit,

00:29:11.086 --> 00:29:14.324
iz derfar geyt men durkh a bisele gringer, az se zol nisht,

00:29:14.324 --> 00:29:18.534
se z- me zol nisht, darfn, zikh aynzinken in ivrit.

00:29:18.534 --> 00:29:22.543
vayl, tsu lernen Yeshaye, tsu lernen Yirmie on ivrit,

00:29:22.543 --> 00:29:26.767
dos iz nish- ⟨me ke-⟩ dos iz nisht, dos ken nit zayn.
